msgstr "/topic Command"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_h.html.heex:9
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Can: kick regular/voiced users, set +v/-v"
msgstr "可:踢普通/voiced用户,设置+v/-v"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_h.html.heex:9
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Cannot: set channel modes, ban users, kick operators or owners"
msgstr "无法: 设置频道模式、 禁止用户、 kick 操作员或所有者"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_i.html.heex:14
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Channel Invites"
msgstr "频道邀请"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_nk.html.heex:21
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Channel Modes Overview"
msgstr "频道模式概览"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_nk.html.heex:8
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Details"
msgstr "细节"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_o.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Grants channel operator status to a user (prefix @). Operators can change channel modes, kick/ban users, and set the topic. They cannot kick owners."
msgstr "给予用户频道操作员身份( 前缀@) 。 操作员可以改变频道模式, kick/ban 用户, 并设置话题. 他们不能踢主人。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_q.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Grants channel owner status to a user (prefix ~). Owners have the highest privilege level and can set any mode, including +o and +q. The first user to join an unregistered channel is automatically made owner."
msgstr "将频道所有者身份授予用户( 前缀 ~) 。 所有者拥有最高的特权级别,可以设置任何模式,包括+o和+q. 第一个加入未注册频道的用户自动成为所有者."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_h.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Grants half-operator status to a user (prefix %). Half-operators can kick users of lower rank and grant/revoke voice (+v), but cannot set channel modes or ban users."
msgstr "向用户授予半操作员地位(前缀%). 半操作者可以踢下级的用户并授予/revoke语音(+v),但不能设置频道模式或禁止用户."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_v.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Grants voice to a user (prefix +), allowing them to speak in moderated (+m) channels. Half-operators and above can grant voice."
msgstr "向用户提供语音(前缀+),允许他们通过主持(+m)频道发言。 半操作者及以上可以授予声音."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_o.html.heex:12
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_q.html.heex:17
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_v.html.heex:12
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Half-Operator (+h)"
msgstr "半操作器 (+h)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_q.html.heex:7
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Hierarchy"
msgstr "等级"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_i.html.heex:18
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Invite Exceptions"
msgstr "邀请例外"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_j.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Limits how many users can join the channel within a time window. Format is count:seconds. For example, +j 5:10 allows 5 joins per 10 seconds. Operators bypass the throttle."
msgstr "限制一个时间窗口内有多少用户可以加入频道. 格式是数:秒。 例如,+j 5:10允许每10秒5次加入. 操作员绕过油门"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_l.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Limits the maximum number of users that can be in the channel."
msgstr "限制频道内的最大用户数量."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_p.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Makes the channel private. Private channels appear in the channel list but with the name shown as \"Prv\" to non-members, hiding the actual channel name. Mutually exclusive with +s (secret)."
msgstr "让频道变得私人化 私人频道出现在频道列表中,但以\"Prv\"为名称向非成员显示,隐藏实际频道名称. 与+s(秘密)相互独占."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_s.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Makes the channel secret. Secret channels do not appear in the channel list (/list) for non-members and are hidden from /whois output. Mutually exclusive with +p (private)."
msgstr "让频道成为秘密 秘密频道不出现在非成员的频道列表(/list)中,并且隐藏在/whois输出中. 与+p(私人)相互独占."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_v.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Moderated (+m)"
msgstr "调制( +m)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_r.html.heex:10
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "NickServ"
msgstr "尼克塞尔"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_q.html.heex:13
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Only other owners can grant or revoke +q."
msgstr "只有其他所有者才能授予或撤销+q."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_h.html.heex:19
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_q.html.heex:16
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Operator (+o)"
msgstr "运算符 (+o)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_h.html.heex:18
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_o.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Owner (+q)"
msgstr "拥有者 (+q)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_q.html.heex:9
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Owner (~) > Operator (@) > Half-Operator (%) > Voice (+) > Regular"
msgstr "拥有者 (~) > 操作者 (@) > 半操作者 (%) > 语音 (+) > 常规"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_h.html.heex:7
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Permissions"
msgstr "权限"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_nk.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Prevents users from sending"
msgstr "防止用户发送"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_s.html.heex:10
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Private (+p)"
msgstr "私人 (+p)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/mode_p.html.heex:10
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Secret (+s)"
msgstr "密语( +s)"

